import { Route, Switch, BrowserRouter, Redirect } from "react-router-dom";
import React from 'react';
import { LoginPage, LogoutPage, Helpers, ErrorPage } from 'core';
import HomePage from "./pages/homePage";
import './assets/app.css'
import DynamicFormPage from './pages/dynamicFormPage'
import FieldsSavePage from "./pages/basePage/fieldsSavePage";
import FormAddPage from "./pages/basePage/formAddPage";
import FormEditPage from "./pages/basePage/formEditPage";
import RequestListPage from "./pages/requestListPage";
import FacilityTypeAddPage from "./pages/basePage/facilityTypeAddPage";
import FacilityTypeEditPage from "./pages/basePage/facilityTypeEditPage";
import FacilityTypetListPage from "./pages/basePage/facilityTypetListPage";;
import LegalCustomerInBranchAdd from "./pages/legalCustomer/legalCustomerInBranchAddPage";
import LegalCustomerInBranchView from "./pages/legalCustomer/legalCustomerInBranchViewPage";
import RequestFormListPage from './pages/requestFormListPage'
import RequestFormSelect from './pages/requestFormSelectPage'
import { GetUrl } from './utils/generals'
import Constants from './utils/constants'
import DropDownAddPage from "./pages/basePage/dropDownAddPage";
import DropDownEditPage from "./pages/basePage/dropDownEditPage";
import DropDownListPage from "./pages/basePage/dropDownListPage";
import DynamicUploadDownloadPage from './pages/dynamicUploadDownloadPage'
import FormListPage from './pages/basePage/formListPage'
import ApprovedFormData from './pages/approvedFormData'
import CustomerAssistant from './pages/customerAssistant'
import ClosingRequestAdd from './pages/closingRequest/closingRequestAdd'
import ClosingRequestList from './pages/closingRequest/closingRequestList'
import ClosingRequestView from './pages/closingRequest/closingRequestView'
import PersonelRegionAdd from './pages/personelRegions/personelRegionAddPage'
import PersonelRegionEdit from './pages/personelRegions/personelRegionEditPage'
import PersonelRegionList from './pages/personelRegions/personelRegionListPage'
import FormVariableRefferenceDataPage from './pages/basePage/formVariableRefferenceDataPage'
import FormFormulaPage from './pages/basePage/formFormulaPage'
import LegalCompanyInfoAddPage from './pages/projects/legalCompanyLoanInfo/legalCompanyInfoAddPage'
import LegalCompanyInfoEditPage from './pages/projects/legalCompanyLoanInfo/legalCompanyInfoEditPage'
import LegalCompanyInfoListPage from './pages/projects/legalCompanyLoanInfo/legalCompanyInfoListPage'
import CompanyLoanInfoPage from './pages/projects/companyLoanInfoPage'
import CompanyDetailLoanInfoPage from './pages/projects/companyDetailLoanInfoPage'
import AverageCompanyAccountBalancePage from './pages/projects/averageCompanyAccountBalancePage'
import ProjectsLoanCalculatorPage from './pages/projects/projectsLoanCalculatorPage'
import PaiedLoanAddPage from './pages/projects/paiedLoan/paiedLoanAddPage'
import PaiedLoanViewPage from './pages/projects/paiedLoan/paiedLoanViewPage'
import PaiedLoanListPage from './pages/projects/paiedLoan/paiedLoanListPage'

const NoAccessMsg = "شما به این بخش دسترسی ندارید و یا زمان نشت شما به پایان رسیده است";
const NoAccessTitle = "عدم دسترسی";

const AppWrapper = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Switch>
        <Route path={ GetUrl("login") } render={(props) => <LoginPage {...props} />} />
        <Route path="/logout" render={(props) => <LogoutPage {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path='/'
          render={(props) => {
            if (Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated()) {
              if (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.AdminCommercialCredits)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser)) {
                if (props.location.search.indexOf("?url=") > -1)
                  return <Redirect to={decodeURIComponent(props.location.search.substring("?url=".length))} />
                return (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser)
                          ? <LegalCompanyInfoListPage {...props} />
                          : <HomePage {...props} />);
              } else {
                return <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } />
              }
            }
            else {
              if (props.location.search.indexOf("?url=") > -1) {
                const r = decodeURIComponent(props.location.search.substring("?url=".length));
                sessionStorage.setItem('redirectUrl', r);
              }
              return <Redirect to={ GetUrl('login') } {...props} />
            }
          }} />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("attachmentAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)) ? (
              <AttachmentAddPage {...props} />
            ) : (
              <Redirect to={ GetUrl("login") } />
            )
          } />

          <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("attachmentEditPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)) ? (
              <AttachmentEditPage {...props} />
            ) : (
              <Redirect to={ GetUrl("login") } />
            )
          } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("fieldsSavePage/:formId?") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <FieldsSavePage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
            
        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("formAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman))
              ? <FormAddPage {...props} />
              : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> }/>

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("formListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman))
            ? <FormListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("formEditPage/:formId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman))
              ? <FormEditPage {...props} />
              : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

       <Route exact path={ GetUrl("requestList") } render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center) ||
                                              Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.AdminCommercialCredits))
                                                  ? (<RequestListPage {...props} /> )
                                                  : (<ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } />)
                                                } />
    
        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('requestFormListPage/:requestId') }
          render={(props) =>
                      Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant) ||
                      Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center))
                              ? <RequestFormListPage {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('requestFormSelect/:requestId') }
          render={(props) => Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                                       Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                       Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                       Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                                       Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center) ||
                                       Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.AdminCommercialCredits))
                              ? <RequestFormSelect {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('dynamicFormPage/:requestId/:formId/:formTitle') }
          render={(props) =>
                        Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center))
                              ? <DynamicFormPage {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('dynamicUploadDownloadPage/:requestId/:requestFormId') }
          render={(props) =>
                        Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant))
                              ? <DynamicUploadDownloadPage {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('approvedFormData') }
          render={(props) =>
                        Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                        Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy))
                              ? <ApprovedFormData {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
              exact
              path={ GetUrl("facilityTypeAddPage") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)) ? (
                  <FacilityTypeAddPage {...props} /> 
                ) : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
            
            <Route
              exact
              path={ GetUrl("facilityTypeEditPage") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)) ? (
                  <FacilityTypeEditPage {...props} /> 
                ) : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
            
            <Route
              exact
              path={ GetUrl("facilityTypetListPage") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)) ? (
                  <FacilityTypetListPage {...props} /> 
                ) : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
            
            <Route exact path={ GetUrl("legalCustomerInBranchAdd") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant))
                  ? <LegalCustomerInBranchAdd {...props} /> 
                  : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

            <Route exact path={ GetUrl("legalCustomerInBranchView/:id") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center))
                  ? <LegalCustomerInBranchView {...props} /> 
                  : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

            <Route exact path={ GetUrl("closingRequestAdd/:requestId/:name") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center))
                  ? <ClosingRequestAdd {...props} /> 
                  : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

            <Route exact path={ GetUrl("closingRequestList") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.RegionManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Center))
                  ? <ClosingRequestList {...props} /> 
                  : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

            <Route exact path={ GetUrl("closingRequestView/:requestId/:name") }
              render={(props) =>
                Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchManager) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchCreditChairman) ||
                                                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.BranchDeputy))
                  ? <ClosingRequestView {...props} /> 
                  : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("dropDownAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
              ? <DropDownAddPage {...props} />
              : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("dropDownEditPage/:dropDownId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
              ? <DropDownEditPage {...props} />
              : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("dropDownListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
              ? <DropDownListPage {...props} />
              : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('customerAssistant') }
          render={(props) =>
                  Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin) ||
                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.Customer) ||
                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.CustomerAssistant))
                        ? <CustomerAssistant {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('personelRegionAdd') }
                  render={(props) =>
                  Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
                        ? <PersonelRegionAdd {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('personelRegionList') }
                  render={(props) =>
                  Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
                        ? <PersonelRegionList {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route exact path={ GetUrl('personelRegionEdit/:personelRegionId') }
                  render={(props) =>
                  Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) ||
                  Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
                        ? <PersonelRegionEdit {...props} /> : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("formVariableRefferenceDataPage/:formId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <FormVariableRefferenceDataPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("formFormulaPage/:formId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <FormFormulaPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("legalCompanyInfoAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <LegalCompanyInfoAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("legalCompanyInfoEditPage/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <LegalCompanyInfoEditPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("legalCompanyInfoListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <LegalCompanyInfoListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("companyLoanInfoPage/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <CompanyLoanInfoPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("companyDetailLoanInfoPage/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <CompanyDetailLoanInfoPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("averageCompanyAccountBalancePage/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <AverageCompanyAccountBalancePage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("projectsLoanCalculator") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <ProjectsLoanCalculatorPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("paiedLoanAddPage/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <PaiedLoanAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("paiedLoanViewPage/:id/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <PaiedLoanViewPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("paiedLoanListPage/:companyInfoId/:companyLoanAccountId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectOfficehUser)
                                              || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.ProjectBranchUser))
            ? <PaiedLoanListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("downlaodFile") }
          render={(props) => {
                                props.history.goBack();
                                window.open('/api/FRQST/Form/DownloadHelp', '_target');
                            } } />

        <Route render={(props) => <ErrorPage {...props} title="صفحه مورد نظر شما در سامانه یافت نشد"
          description="صفحه مورد نظر شما در سامانه حذف شده است یا احتمالا شما مجوز لازم جهت دسترسی به صفحه مذکور را ندارید" />} />
      </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  );
};

export default AppWrapper;
